      In [10]:
      x
      outlier_counts = {}
      for col in numerical_cols:
          Q1 = df[col].quantile(0.25)
          Q3 = df[col].quantile(0.75)
          IQR = Q3 - Q1
          lower = Q1 - 1.5 * IQR
          upper = Q3 + 1.5 * IQR
          outlier_counts[col] = ((df[col] < lower) | (df[col] > upper)).sum()
      pd.Series(outlier_counts).sort_values(ascending=False)

      In [11]:
      x
      df["outlier_flag"] = 0
      for col in numerical_cols:
          Q1 = df[col].quantile(0.25)
          Q3 = df[col].quantile(0.75)
          IQR = Q3 - Q1
          lower = Q1 - 1.5 * IQR
          upper = Q3 + 1.5 * IQR
          df.loc[(df[col] < lower) | (df[col] > upper), "outlier_flag"] = 1
      df["outlier_flag"].value_counts()

      In [12]:
      x
      df_clean = df.copy()
      for col in numerical_cols:
          Q1 = df_clean[col].quantile(0.25)
          Q3 = df_clean[col].quantile(0.75)
          IQR = Q3 - Q1
          lower = Q1 - 1.5 * IQR
          upper = Q3 + 1.5 * IQR
          df_clean[col] = np.clip(df_clean[col], lower, upper)
